window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Why do the worst cases always start with anonymous calls?</p> <p>I should have just kept ignoring my phone. Just like I've been doing for the last couple months. It's been a concerted effort, since my investigation skills are in demand after a string of high-profile cases. But I haven't been interested in more business.</p> <p>I've been more focused on other things.</p> <p>Too bad Serena Adams doesn't care what I want.</p> <p>Hell, she doesn't even want to hire me.</p> <p>She just wants me to know that three bodies are going to drop today.</p> <p>And that after the tally hits three . . . I'm next.</p>"; 
